  <body>
    <center><h1>Cloudy Day</h1><center>
	<h2>Poem</h2>
	<audio controls autoplay>
	  <source src="Uudam - Mother in the dream - 梦中的额吉.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
	      Your browser does not support the audio element.
	</audio>
	<p>
	  Sometimes<br>
	  When you're <a href="http://www.reactiongifs.com/r/has-a-sad.gif">feeling down</a><br>
	  You <a href="https://i2.wp.com/gifrific.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/baby-wolf-lies-down.gif?ssl=1">lay down</a> on the grass<br>
	  And stare, <a href="http://illusion.scene360.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/flavio-apel-03.jpg">eyes wide open</a><br>
	  At the endless sky above<br><br>

	  A gust of wind <a href="https://media.giphy.com/media/4VzpkC4Zze7rW/giphy-downsized-large.gif">sweeps</a> through the flat expanse of empty grassland<br>
	  Tall grasses tangle in your <a href="https://media.tenor.com/images/70598dcad05c7df1cbb67fd7142f5270/tenor.gif">disheveled hair</a><br>
	  Your eyes are wide open<br>
	  Searching for meaning, yet <a href="http://gifimage.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/blinking-eyes-gif-13.gif">searching aimlessly</a><br>
	  In the sky above<br><br>

	  It is a cloudy day<br>
	  And that satisfies you<br>
	  A <a href="https://media.giphy.com/media/V5EkPVDbEzw9a/giphy.gif">blue sky</a> is beautiful but boring<br>
	  Vast but uniform<br>
	  Inoffensive and uninspiring<br><br>

	  But the cloudy day<br>
	  Is nuanced, layered<br>
	  You stare into a cacophony of <a href="http://www.texturex.com/albums/Sky-Textures/cloud%20texture%20above%20clouds%20fairy%20tale%20sky%20texture.jpg">textured billows</a><br>
	  A painter's palette of white, gray, and <a href="https://78.media.tumblr.com/32bd8387a7a810b07015a3f1dd412f26/tumblr_p14gymgDVX1tntn9qo1_500.gif">violent purple</a><br>
	  You still may not be happy<br><br>

	  But you are <a href="https://celluloidwickerman.files.wordpress.com/2015/08/gif-2.gif">comforted</a>
	</p>
	
  </body>
</html>

